data.description: OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY 12/16/23 12:00PM-2:00PM!!! Welcome to 13880 Muirfield Ct, a remarkable property located on the 7th hole of Broadlands Golf Course in The Broadlands neighborhood. It is a true peaceful oasis! This beautiful, bright, and airy 5 bed, 5 bath home in Broomfield offers comfortable, functional living with plenty of natural light throughout the home. Exterior features include a 3-car garage, beautifully landscaped yard with a beautiful patio off of kitchen/family room area overlooking the golf course.  Interior features include a private office near the front of the home, living room and formal dining room great for holidays and entertaining. The gourmet kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances including a new gas cooktop range, an oversized island and nook area with endless views of the golf course, a beautiful way to start each day!  Mudroom/laundry room right off the 3-car garage with great storage.   Upstairs you will find the spacious primary bedroom overlooking the golf course and is a true retreat with a 5-piece bath and an oversized walk-in closet. 3 additional bedrooms upstairs with 2 additional bathrooms. The finished basement has a generously sized family room, workout space and guest bedroom and full bathroom. Upgrades to the home include but not limited to, Interior paint throughout home, new hardwood floors throughout main level, new carpet throughout, new lighting, all door hardware and hinges have been replaced, new light fixtures, new gas cooktop and refrigerator, professedly landscaped front and back yard including sprinkler system update. Water Heater and A/C replaced in 2021, humidifier added in 2022. Neighborhood amenities include parks, trails, community pool, clubhouse.  Golf course views from every window in the back of the home!  From its beautiful natural landscapes to its friendly community atmosphere, The Broadlands is an ideal place to call home. Come take a look!
